name: Fat Publisher
overview:
At Fatpublisher we want to enhance peoples lives by creating wonderful online experiences. Customers are attracted to online businesses that build a memorable experience into their products and services. Customers wish to be understood by business and they want business to shape their products, services and service delivery in a way that makes them feel good. Fatpublisher understand this and we make it happen.

The web presents an opportunity for connection, communication and collaboration. Fatpublisher’s vision is a web free of limitations, that encourages creativity, sharing and is a place for entrepreneurs to realise the full value of their ideas. Our vision is a web where businesses can find new ways of reaching their goals and their customers.
